Story: User wants to add local water fountain (which isn't shown in the app) to database for other users to see 
  1. Ask user to select the building or enter the location (we will manually select the building)
    - Good Path: location is valid
      Continue
    - Bad Path: location is invalid
      Throw error message and request new location
  2. User must input floor and mark the spot on the building map. 
    - Good Path: data user inputted is valid
      Create new water fountain in database and then bring user back to home
    - Bad Path: data user inputted is invalid
      Request user to reinput data
      
